'''Joseph Runzo''' is an American professor publishing mainly in the area of a global [[philosophy of religion]]. He is currently Life Fellow at [[Clare Hall, Cambridge|Clare Hall]], [[Cambridge University]].{{Citation needed|date=May 2010}}
